{"tid":2281183,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★Nokia 8000 4G 曝光 預載 Facebook 和 WhatsApp!","createTime":"2020-11-11T05:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T09:51:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7d4436bdf5289bb1b1afb7eb684ccc726d01fadb","tid":2281183,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:04:30.000Z","msg":"Nokia 8000 4G 將會以高階設計作招徠，其機身用上類似玻璃的物料製造，按鍵亦用上 3D 弧形設計。跟之前上市的 Nokia 2720 Flip 和 Nokia 8110 4G 一樣，Nokia 8000 4G 將會採用 KaiOS 系統，預載 Facebook 和 WhatsApp 程式，而且擁有 Wi-Fi 熱點功能。<br />\n<br />\n規格方面，Nokia 8000 4G 配備 2.8 吋 QVGA 解像度 LCD 螢幕，搭配 Snapdragon 210 處理器、512MB RAM 和 4GB 儲存（支援 microSD 擴充）。Nokia 8000 4G 支援 4G 雙卡、Wi-Fi 和藍牙，可拆式電池用量為 1,500mAh，機背有一枚 2MP 相機鏡頭。雖然 WinFuture 已經上載了產品照和宣傳照，但未知 Nokia 8000 4G 的實際發佈日期。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZAp7JXG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZAp7JXG.jpg&h=86c88d68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/11/11/nokia-8000-4g-leaked/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F11%2F11%2Fnokia-8000-4g-leaked%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=6f5b4be6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/11/11/nokia-8000-4g-leaked/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"32d1ffea6cbcfcc71b92bc4580bf7c56a7edeb99","tid":2281183,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/avjSU4x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FavjSU4x.png&h=538c187b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da736978d2260c700ce833a91f7da8a63f6b64d1","tid":2281183,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmo